1
00:00:00,050 --> 00:00:03,000
Day 2 earned me 3 cents.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:06,402
But the real cost was the three things I found.

3
00:00:06,402 --> 00:00:07,833
I can't code.

4
00:00:07,833 --> 00:00:10,027
9 years in crypto.

5
00:00:10,027 --> 00:00:13,763
I gave AI a thousand dollars to trade for me.

6
00:00:13,763 --> 00:00:14,875
Day 2.

7
00:00:14,875 --> 00:00:24,083
Around noon it placed its first real trade — bought one SOL contract at eighty-two seventy-six, sold it minutes later.

8
00:00:24,083 --> 00:00:28,569
Balance went from one thousand to nine ninety-nine oh three.

9
00:00:28,569 --> 00:00:31,180
Fees took 97 cents.

10
00:00:31,180 --> 00:00:33,111
Sounds like nothing, right?

11
00:00:33,111 --> 00:00:38,472
But in those two minutes of watching, I noticed three things I'd been pretending not to see.

12
00:00:38,472 --> 00:00:40,847
One — the grid module.

13
00:00:40,847 --> 00:00:42,623
Supposed to be live.

14
00:00:42,623 --> 00:00:44,847
Still simulating orders.

15
00:00:44,847 --> 00:00:48,402
I'd thought about whether this might break when I wrote the spec.

16
00:00:48,402 --> 00:00:50,361
I decided probably not.

17
00:00:50,361 --> 00:00:55,555
Two — seven of my backend servers bound to zero-zero-zero-zero.

18
00:00:55,555 --> 00:00:57,805
Open to the entire internet.

19
00:00:57,805 --> 00:00:59,027
For a week.

20
00:00:59,027 --> 00:01:01,000
Nothing bad had happened.

21
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:05,527
But nothing bad yet isn't the same as nothing bad ever.

22
00:01:05,527 --> 00:01:09,472
Three — a source file I'd pushed to public GitHub.

23
00:01:09,472 --> 00:01:11,736
My phone number, hardcoded.

24
00:01:11,736 --> 00:01:16,611
A three-cent profit exposed three pieces of work I'd been avoiding.

25
00:01:16,611 --> 00:01:19,333
In paper mode you never see these.

26
00:01:19,333 --> 00:01:23,858
Real skin on the line is the only thing that shows them to you.

27
00:01:23,858 --> 00:01:28,486
Day 3 tomorrow — I decided to give everything away for free.

28
00:01:28,486 --> 00:01:29,861
Follow along.

